🎬 LeafLearning — 40s Promo Ad Script

Style: Clean, fast-paced, dark/light academic UI, kinetic typography
Music: Modern, calm but energetic (soft synth + beat)

⏱ 0:00–0:03 — Hook (CRITICAL)

Visual

Dark background

Text types in fast:

“Studying shouldn’t feel impossible.”

Text glitches slightly → fades.

Why this exists:
You must emotionally hook before explaining features. This targets stress immediately.

⏱ 0:03–0:07 — Problem: Information Overload

Visual

Student UI

Hundreds of pages scrolling fast

Highlighted text everywhere

On-screen text (big, bold):

“Hundreds of pages.”
“Zero clarity.”

Small subtext:

Textbooks. Notes. PDFs. Slides.

Why:
Visual overload mirrors the student’s mental state.

⏱ 0:07–0:11 — Problem: Time & Stress

Visual

Clock spinning

Student dashboard showing “17 hrs/week”

Stress meter filling up

On-screen text:

“17+ hours wasted every week.”

Then quickly:

“Only 20% retained.”

Why:
Numbers build credibility and urgency.

⏱ 0:11–0:14 — Product Reveal

Visual

Clean transition

LeafLearning logo appears

UI slides into view

On-screen text (center):

LeafLearning
Study Smarter with AI

Why:
This is the relief moment. Clean, calm visuals.

⏱ 0:14–0:20 — Core Magic (FAST)

Visual sequence (rapid cuts):

PDF uploaded

AI highlights concepts

Summary appears

Flashcards auto-generate

Quiz created instantly

On-screen text (syncs with visuals):

Upload anything.
Get summaries.
Flashcards.
Quizzes.
In seconds.

Small text:

With academic citations.

Why:
This is the “wow” section. No explanation — just results.

⏱ 0:20–0:25 — Smart Studying

Visual

Spaced repetition calendar

Progress graph going up

Retention % increasing

On-screen text:

“Study less.”
“Remember more.”

Then:

“AI-powered spaced repetition.”

Why:
Connects effort → outcome. This is what students actually want.

⏱ 0:25–0:29 — Audience Callout

Visual

Quick cuts:

Medical notes

Law case files

Engineering formulas

On-screen text (stacked):

Medical Students
Law Students
Engineering Students

Then:

“Built for serious studying.”

Why:
Students must see themselves using it.

⏱ 0:29–0:33 — Social Proof

Visual

Numbers animate up

Stars fill in

On-screen text:

125,000+ documents processed
45,000+ study hours saved
4.9★ student rating

Why:
Removes skepticism right before pricing.

⏱ 0:33–0:36 — Pricing (Very Important)

Visual

Tokens floating softly

“No Subscription” stamp

On-screen text:

No subscriptions.
No hidden fees.

Then:

500 free tokens to start.

Why:
Destroys the #1 student objection: commitment.

